net.fabricmc.fabric.api.client.render.fluid.v1

Interface FluidRenderHandlerRegistry


  • public interface FluidRenderHandlerRegistry
    Registry for FluidRenderHandler instances. Notably, this supports querying, overriding and wrapping vanilla fluid rendering.
